data.description:
Welcome to the epitome of modern living in this remarkable paired home, offering the lifestyle of new construction with the added charm of thoughtful upgrades. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, including an unfinished basement awaiting your personal touch, this home is designed for both comfort and convenience.
Nestled on a sprawling corner lot with a generous backyard, enjoy ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. With over $40,000 in upgrades meticulously added after the owners moved in, every aspect of this home exudes quality and style.
Step outside onto the covered deck or extended stamped concrete patio, perfect for enjoying al fresco dining or soaking up the sunshine. Inside, the open floor plan welcomes you with abundant natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout.
The heart of the home, the kitchen, features a sprawling island and ample space for a dining area, perfect for culinary adventures and entertaining guests. A large walk-in pantry provides additional storage and organization.
Upstairs, discover a fantastic bonus space, offering endless possibilities for a home office, playroom, or relaxation area. Each of the spacious bedrooms boasts its own walk-in closet, ensuring comfort and convenience for all occupants.
Move-in ready and conveniently located near parks and amenities, this paired home offers the perfect blend of elegance, functionality, and modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your new home sweet home!
